<P>__{(bowing)}
<D>__{i thank you. my wife thanks you. my unborn child thanks you.}
<A>__{mikey moves his rail of chips to the felt.}
<C>__{mikey}
<D>__{color me up will ya?}
<A>__{larry notices shelly slipping on a pair of leather gloves.}
<C>__{larry}
<D>__{you've gotta be kidding me.}
<P>__{(off shelly's steely glare)}
<D>__{that's not how i propose we handle it. we'll turn the matter over to the authorities. they'll be blacklisted, their credit ruined...}
<C>__{shelly}
<P>__{(gets in larry's face)}
<D>__{and then we'll give 'em both a lollipop for the ride home. come watch and learn, harvard. a little lesson on how to protect your investment the old school way.}
