<D>__{why don't we go do this in my office? i don't like to hand out all this amount of cash on the floor.}
<A>__{security (tony and lou) corrals the couple. leads them away. bernie watches as they pass by. mikey looks into bernie's eyes. they both know he's been made. natalie doesn't say anything, just looks at bernie.}
